                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4453" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1114</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8746 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随机应变：蓝海酒店集团的实习生招聘与管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Trim the Sails：Intern Recruitment and Management of Blue Horizon Hotel Group(BHG) </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘涛，徐福英</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东工商学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东蓝海酒店管理股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蓝海酒店集团；实习生；单体招聘单体管理；整体招聘混合管理；混合招聘混合管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Blue Horizon Hotel Group; intern; independent recruitment and independent management; overall recruitment and mixed management; mixed recruitment and mixed management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了山东蓝海酒店集团根据内外经营环境的变化而不断调整和优化自身的实习生招聘与管理模式。在2006年之前，由于集团分店数量少，经营地域集中且人力资源供应较为充分，故采取了单体招聘单体管理模式；但在2006年以后，随着分店数量的快速增加和经营区域的扩张以及市场竞争的加剧，为提高实习生招聘竞争力和管理水平，蓝海集团开始实施整体招聘混合管理模式，并围绕该模式进行了相应的组织结构设计、业务流程优化以及内部政策支持。随着蓝海集团正由单一区域性酒店集团转向多区域性酒店集团，整体招聘的弊端开始显现，集团采取了相应措施加以优化，包括由整体招聘转向混合招聘，合理地进行内部分工以及完善招聘人员的职业生涯规划等。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes that Blue Horizon Hotel Group continuously adjusts and optimizes its intern recruitment and management mode according to the changes of internal and external business environment. Before 2006, BHG adopted the independent recruitment and independent management mode due to the small number of branches, concentrated business areas and sufficient supply of human resources. Due to the fast rise of branches and the expansion of business areas and the intensification of market competition, the overall recruitment and mixed management pattern has been implemented in order to improve the recruitment competitiveness and management level of interns after 2006. Furthermore, BHG has carried on the corresponding organization structure design, work flow design and internal policy support according to the implementation of the above mode. However, the drawbacks of overall recruitment are emerging accompanying with the shifting from a single regional hotel group to a multi-regional hotel group. BHG is taking some countermeasures to optimize the above drawbacks, which include the transition from overall recruitment to mixed recruitment, reasonable internal division within recruitment department, and the improvement of recruitment personnel selection and career planning.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《旅游企业战略管理》、《旅游企业人力资源管理》、《酒店管理概论》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-04</td>
                            </tr>
